# 🎯 Tooltip Hover Transition for Social Media Icons

This is a small HTML & CSS project that displays a set of animated social media icons with hover-enabled tooltips using only HTML and CSS. Each icon reveals a tooltip with a smooth transition effect, making the UI visually interactive and fun.

## 🚀 Features

- Animated tooltip on hover using pure CSS
- Custom accent color for each icon
- Minimal, responsive layout using Flexbox
- Clean and modern design using Poppins font

